Package JFiles.Constants

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Email
    Constants related to Email service
    There are 3 types of email could be generated - after registration, in case of password reset (by admin), in case user updates his information
    Page
    Paths to JSP pages which are stored into WEB-INF jsp folder
    Role
    Role value and role name
    There are 3 types of access
    USER - without access to Admin menu
    ADMIN - limited access to Admin menu (he is able to reset password for any user and view or download User and Statistics tables
    SUPER_ADMIN - is able to edit User and Statistics tables (Developer role)
    Table
    Parameters of tables which could be displayed from Admin menu
    XO
    Constants related to XO game
    X, O, BLANK - game filed constants - cross, zero, nothing
    FIELD_SIZE, WIN_LINE_SIZE - Size of game field, Qty of X or O in a row to win game
    WIN, LOOSE, EVEN - ids of game result
